item.title: Project 1-Exploratory Data Analysis
item.description: Javier Granados II, jg65347 Introduction library(tidyverse) library(dplyr) library(knitr) library(ggplot2) library(fivethirtyeight) mlbpt <- mlb_as_play_talent mlbtt <- mlb_as_team_talent October, a month for everything Halloween and fall, from scary movies to pumpkin spice lattes. But for baseball fanatics, October means playoffs for Major League Baseball. Every pitch counts, leaving thousands of fans and players holding their breath every time the ball is thrown to home plate. Only the best of the best teams make it to October, with the exception of two- the American and National League All-Star Teams.
